Module org.klojang.check
Package org.klojang.check.fallible

Interface FallibleSupplier<T,X extends Throwable>

Type Parameters:
T - The type of the return value
X - The type of the exception potentially being thrown
Functional Interface:
This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.
@FunctionalInterface public interface FallibleSupplier<T,X extends Throwable>
An alternative to the Supplier interface that allows the functional method to throw a checked exception.
Author:
Ayco Holleman
